"""
        Test the merging method without the strict mode.
        """
nd_dict = {'hello': ['hello', 'Uhh'], 'hello_world': {'author': 'nobody',
    'surname': 'body'}}
expected = {'hello': ['This is Funilrys!', 'Uhh!', 'hello', 'Uhh'], 'world':
    'Fun Ilrys', 'hello_world': {'author': 'nobody', 'name': 'Fun',
    'surname': 'body'}}
actual = Dict(self.st_dict).merge(nd_dict, strict=False)
self.assertEqual(expected, actual)
